messages.message: Second problem they ran into was that they ended up in the ‘My Hub’ section, created an app and were stuck with the output from their app. For us insiders we have the curse of knowledge and understand deeply what building an app means, but this was entirely new to them and they got completely lost and couldn’t figure out why they couldn’t _converse_ or that they were in a ‘build’ mode of the app and could back out to get to ‘converse’ model. I won’t make suggestions here, just sharing their experience.
